quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"By the horses making charge, snorting"
  100,2,"and the producers of sparks, striking (their horseshoe)"
  100,3,and the attackers in the morning
  100,4,that raise cloud of dust with it
  100,5,and penetrate to the middle of it (the battle) together
  100,6,indeed the human being is ungrateful to his Master
  100,7,and he is certainly a witness to that
  100,8,and indeed his love for the good things (and wealth) is extreme
  100,9,"Does he not know that, when what is in the graves is turned upside down"
  100,10,and what is in the chests is exposed
  100,11,indeed their Master is well aware of them on that day